{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, RL-based models can accommodate the modeling complexities but require a huge amount of data to ensure the consistence of performance under uncertainties.",
    "The current research trends have been the combination of MPC and RL so as to enjoy both of their pros.",
    "The researches are mainly in the following two aspects.",
    "One is to use ML to mimic the control policies output by MPC controllers.",
    "Specifically, the control of MPC controllers can be regarded as the parameterized policy with respect to the disturbance."
  ]
}